</prolog>
<body>
<section id="description">
</section>
<ol id="conformance">
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.ihe.doc/classes/Medication.html">IHE Medication</xref> template (templateId: <tt>1.3.6.1.4.1.19376.1.5.3.1.4.7</tt>)</li>
</ol>
<ol id="aggregate">
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.hl7.rim.doc/classes/InfrastructureRoot.html">RIM Infrastructure Root</xref></li>
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.hl7.rim.doc/classes/Act.html">RIM Act</xref></li>
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.doc/classes/ClinicalStatement.html">CDA Clinical Statement</xref></li>
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.doc/classes/SubstanceAdministration.html">CDA Substance Administration</xref></li>
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.ccd.doc/classes/MedicationActivity.html">CCD Medication Activity</xref> template (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.24</tt>)</li>
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.ihe.doc/classes/Medication.html">IHE Medication</xref> template (templateId: <tt>1.3.6.1.4.1.19376.1.5.3.1.4.7</tt>)</li>
<li>[CCD] <b>SHALL</b> contain [1..*] <tt>id</tt></li>
<li>[CCD] <b>SHOULD</b> contain [0..1] <tt>statusCode</tt></li>
<li>[CCD] <b>MAY</b> contain [0..1] <tt>entryRelationship</tt>, such that it<ol>
<li>contains <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.ccd.doc/classes/MedicationSeriesNumberObservation.html">CCD Medication Series Number Observation</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.46</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li>[CCD] <b>MAY</b> contain [0..1] <tt>entryRelationship</tt>, such that it<ol>
<li>contains <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.ccd.doc/classes/MedicationStatusObservation.html">CCD Medication Status Observation</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.47</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li>[CCD] <b>MAY</b> contain [0..*] <tt>entryRelationship</tt>, such that it<ol>
<li>has @typeCode="SUBJ" <i>SUBJ (has subject)</i></li>
<li>contains <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.ccd.doc/classes/PatientInstruction.html">CCD Patient Instruction</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.49</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li>[CCD] <b>SHALL</b> satisfy: <codeblock>self.moodCode=vocab::x_DocumentSubstanceMood::EVN or self.moodCode=vocab::x_DocumentSubstanceMood::INT </codeblock></li>
</ol>
